{
  "info": {
    "name": "Viamatica - Sistema de Gestión de Caja",
    "description": "Colección de la prueba técnica (Node.js + Angular).\n\nCÓMO USARLA:\n1. Levanta el backend (puerto 3000).\n2. Ejecuta 'Auth > Login (admin)': el token JWT se guarda automáticamente en la variable {{token}} y el resto de peticiones lo usan.\n3. Para probar permisos por rol, ejecuta el login del gestor o del cajero.\n\nUsuarios demo: admin1234/Admin1234, gestor123/Gestor123, cajero123/Cajero123",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Guarda el token automáticamente. Acepta username o email. Se bloquea al 3er intento fallido.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"admin1234\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin1234\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado para el resto de peticiones');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (gestor)",
